title: Complete Dead - All of the Evil Dead trilogy edited to one movie
description: I have taken the original Trilogy and edited them together. From begriming to end of Evil Dead 1. Then Evil Dead 2 cut out the begriming until you get to point where camera zooms in on Ash. Then the rest of Evil dead 2. Then edit the end of evil dead 2 where the explosion occurs. Finally edited off the begriming of Army of Darkness to the point where explosion and Ash is thrown to the ground  with the 1973 yellow Oldsmobile Delta 88 automobile
